name: Evan Michael
text: I like this location because I order online and they always have my order ready for the time I schedule. It's inappropriate to rate the food as it is a chain.

name: Eleni Carr
text: This Place is so great! Very Friendly staff

name: Cory Seaman
text: People might be more inclined to visit this slowly dying chain if the stores made half an effort to hide it.
